
*Assignment No: 1*

Sub: Cloud Computing        Date: 06-8-2025           Deadline: 15-8-25


Q.1 Explain the concept of cloud service deployment models (Public, Private, Hybrid, and Community) and analyze a real-world scenario where a hybrid cloud approach would be more beneficial than a pure public or private cloud. Justify your reasoning with technical and business considerations.

Q.2 Discuss the role of virtualization in cloud computing. How does virtualization enable resource abstraction and scalability in cloud environments? Additionally, compare virtualization with containerization and explain when you would choose one over the other in cloud-native application development.
